{"tid":1811450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終極和你攬抄 顛覆香港經濟生態","createTime":"2020-01-04T16:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T15:59:16.000Z","uid":131839,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"34f20bd40b9ba87b44a78c84825a9cc4a0e2eb61","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"眾所尻知係做成香港呢個畸型社會局面 <br />\n除左政府仆街外 地產商都同樣仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到樓價咁撚高 大部分香港人為左買間屋住 死慳死掋去儲首期去供樓<br />\n為左個磚頭 逼住做份唔鐘意既工 就連老細on9都要扮死狗擦佢鞋<br />\n大家有無諗過其實自己的樓可以自己起<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈既極致就係連樓我都起撚埋 打倒地產霸權<br />\n想像一下宜家有層樓 成棟都係手足一齊住<br />\n樓下有幾間地鋪 可以做下茶記 賣下雜貨 開間小食店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成棟野都唔撚用支那貨 有本地用本地 無本地用台灣/外國<br />\n請人就請撚曬手足 呢個畫面幾靚<br />\n講完都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦 FF完 究竟件事實行上黎係點 需要D咩呢?<br />\n<br />\n首先我地要知起樓個成本要點計<br />\n根據上網搵到立法會既文件<br />\n物業發展總成本= 地價+物業發展權費+建築成本+項目預備工程成本+ 融資成本+ 市場推廣成本+ 專業服務費用及其他<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/bc/bc03/papers/bc030920cb1-2237-2c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr05-06%2Fchinese%2Fbc%2Fbc03%2Fpapers%2Fbc030920cb1-2237-2c.pdf&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=042c55a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/bc/bc03/papers/bc030920cb1-2237-2c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n我將佢簡化就係<br />\n物業發展總成本= 地價+建築成本+其他<br />\n<br />\n咁買塊地皮又需要幾多錢呢 睇返近幾年既小型地皮拍賣<br />\n2011年 紅磡內地段第555號佔582.3平方米既地皮就賣左4億6百萬<br />\n而個地方就發展左宜家既城中匯<br />\n城中匯有25層 一共提供左95個實用面積約由410至423平方呎既單位<br />\n當佢全部410呎啦 總共有95*410=38950<br />\n參考網上資料普通私樓既建築成本的每呎（不包括地價）約3,000多元<br />\n即係話計左地皮個價 4億/38950 + 3000 = ~13000<br />\n而呢個價係仲未計停車場既價位<br />\n當日呢個樓盤係賣緊呎價平均為16000<br />\n講緊發展商係賺左起碼2成<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我地成為良心發展商 將個利潤減到最底<br />\n咁樣就幫輕好多香港既置業問題<br />\n只要唔洗為左層樓做乾弟 其實香港人做既工種可以好多樣性<br />\n香港人可以真正發揮佢既創意 <br />\n香港人可以真係搞創科<br />\n香港人可以提供好優質既教育等等等<br />\n<br />\n當然呢個只係個諗法 入邊有好多困難<br />\n1. 籌集資金<br />\n2. 負責人<br />\n3. 成立公司?<br />\n3. 投標問題<br />\n<br />\n不過太易做就一早就有人做左啦<br />\n但呢半年我見到好多奇蹟 無野係無可能既<br />\n大家覺得有得諗既就傾下啦<br />\ntg:@fuckhkp<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f17441126fb221271124682703e2204bc8e38500","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:51:39.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"af88ef4f42a79ffba3aca9c695f1fc58cc88db42","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:51:49.000Z","msg":"再推再推"},{"pid":"1797ee8234d517e40fb7e991ad2e3d438d9ffa59","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"再黎"},{"pid":"eaf7c6d577f3448253b6b7265aa6d1e9dcf4af08","tid":1811450,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:53:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38a357a165a376a816c795a1cb4c1658735c76f8","tid":1811450,"uid":271756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:55:29.000Z","msg":"其實唔好戇鳩啦，人地發展商起樓要時間，所以先要賺個價，甚至係往後幾年溢價，呢個唔係良心問題，係正常操作！個問題喺地價度"},{"pid":"91ede8e1fff51c851b00ca4157756cb7e1ff624e","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:55:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"069b7f32535bfe2d02ea23ae361e648925c7e273","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T23:55:19.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"cdd11ef6f321eea3b28cf72d876d12fa37b41d40","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:44:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97b2750f14be4f892fda53341dacf1181124fe22","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d319ccc45d74bc62412caa9e950724b36dd85a97","tid":1811450,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"你投地，中資用錢抬你價，抬到你玩唔起"},{"pid":"12a8ec5a0f24c7183d986556110b29abe9e9a1c7","tid":1811450,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:08:48.000Z","msg":"認真，無乜可能成事"},{"pid":"929b4fb8b1b85ed2e67751ec433dd9e49517d6b7","tid":1811450,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立 唯一出路</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中國肺炎</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad82a53f959bd5b87c9de30e3f7474c85c3ea94","tid":1811450,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲港豬請入！元氣搞優惠！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813301</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4b4d72b8a6f38965f94f895bfab4a49a45d2e6d","tid":1811450,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"FF上腦?<br />\n<br />\n做地盤十個有六個新移民<br />\n<br />\n如果你請全部香港人幫你起<br />\n<br />\n二千萬可能只可以買三百呎"},{"pid":"9165a8315f871d745d7b17007322e5d847396230","tid":1811450,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"當然如果做到就梗係最好啦，不過要面對好多發展商啊地產商啦佢哋勾結，但我讚成搞返個黃色地產商與其將啲錢比大財團不如益返自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db889946d3b9deea0719bdae790371b834cfb721","tid":1811450,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34f20bd40b9ba87b44a78c84825a9cc4a0e2eb61","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:51:26.000Z","msg":"眾所尻知係做成香港呢個畸型社會局面 <br />\n除左政府仆街外 地產商都同樣仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到樓價咁撚高 大部分香港人為左買間屋住 死慳死掋去儲首期去供樓<br />\n為左個磚頭 逼住做份唔鐘意既工 就連老細on9都要扮死狗擦佢鞋<br />\n大家有無諗過其實自己的樓可以自己起<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈既極致就係連樓我都起撚埋 打倒地產霸權<br />\n想像一下宜家有層樓 成棟都係手足一齊住<br />\n樓下有幾間地鋪 可以做下茶記 賣下雜貨 開間小食店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成棟野都唔撚用支那貨 有本地用本地 無本地用台灣/外國<br />\n請人就請撚曬手足 呢個畫面幾靚<br />\n講完都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦 FF完 究竟件事實行上黎係點 需要D咩呢?<br />\n<br />\n首先我地要知起樓個成本要點計<br />\n根據上網搵到立法會既文件<br />\n物業發展總成本= 地價+物業發展權費+建築成本+項目預備工程成本+ 融資成本+ 市場推廣成本+ 專業服務費用及其他<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/bc/bc03/papers/bc030920cb1-2237-2c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr05-06%2Fchinese%2Fbc%2Fbc03%2Fpapers%2Fbc030920cb1-2237-2c.pdf&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=042c55a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr05-06/chinese/bc/bc03/papers/bc030920cb1-2237-2c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n我將佢簡化就係<br />\n物業發展總成本= 地價+建築成本+其他<br />\n<br />\n咁買塊地皮又需要幾多錢呢 睇返近幾年既小型地皮拍賣<br />\n2011年 紅磡內地段第555號佔582.3平方米既地皮就賣左4億6百萬<br />\n而個地方就發展左宜家既城中匯<br />\n城中匯有25層 一共提供左95個實用面積約由410至423平方呎既單位<br />\n當佢全部410呎啦 總共有95*410=38950<br />\n參考網上資料普通私樓既建築成本的每呎（不包括地價）約3,000多元<br />\n即係話計左地皮個價 4億/38950 + 3000 = ~13000<br />\n而呢個價係仲未計停車場既價位<br />\n當日呢個樓盤係賣緊呎價平均為16000<br />\n講緊發展商係賺左起碼2成<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要我地成為良心發展商 將個利潤減到最底<br />\n咁樣就幫輕好多香港既置業問題<br />\n只要唔洗為左層樓做乾弟 其實香港人做既工種可以好多樣性<br />\n香港人可以真正發揮佢既創意 <br />\n香港人可以真係搞創科<br />\n香港人可以提供好優質既教育等等等<br />\n<br />\n當然呢個只係個諗法 入邊有好多困難<br />\n1. 籌集資金<br />\n2. 負責人<br />\n3. 成立公司?<br />\n3. 投標問題<br />\n<br />\n不過太易做就一早就有人做左啦<br />\n但呢半年我見到好多奇蹟 無野係無可能既<br />\n大家覺得有得諗既就傾下啦<br />\ntg:@fuckhkp<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"米埔果頭買農地起小棟開始?"},{"pid":"ef52c77ec1c235962fe4b8b7ae8ca1c47605a488","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d319ccc45d74bc62412caa9e950724b36dd85a97","tid":1811450,"uid":122709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"你投地，中資用錢抬你價，抬到你玩唔起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"除左投地 係咪私人地產商都係間唔中放下d細地出黎？"},{"pid":"309a02a96ef998385a28911109d9daef74f07d69","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b4d72b8a6f38965f94f895bfab4a49a45d2e6d","tid":1811450,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"FF上腦?<br />\n<br />\n做地盤十個有六個新移民<br />\n<br />\n如果你請全部香港人幫你起<br />\n<br />\n二千萬可能只可以買三百呎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"其實地盤工幾好賺架 點解香港人唔可以自己做返"},{"pid":"803d8879327eb2da13de7733aabaf7ecaa4b22ee","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9165a8315f871d745d7b17007322e5d847396230","tid":1811450,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"當然如果做到就梗係最好啦，不過要面對好多發展商啊地產商啦佢哋勾結，但我讚成搞返個黃色地產商與其將啲錢比大財團不如益返自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"岩啊 我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24cadacee6442856988d0e3b1691786756cf8f6","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db889946d3b9deea0719bdae790371b834cfb721","tid":1811450,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34f20bd40b9ba87b44a78c84825a9cc4a0e2eb61","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply