eplyTime":"2020-01-06T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"米埔果頭買農地起小棟開始?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"無錯 就係由細地做起"},{"pid":"791f51cdd2c4d15a8907a6055ceec86a9ee9d9e2","tid":1811450,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"309a02a96ef998385a28911109d9daef74f07d69","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b4d72b8a6f38965f94f895bfab4a49a45d2e6d","tid":1811450,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"FF上腦?<br />\n<br />\n做地盤十個有六個新移民<br />\n<br />\n如果你請全部香港人幫你起<br />\n<br />\n二千萬可能只可以買三百呎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"其實地盤工幾好賺架 點解香港人唔可以自己做返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"揸的士都兩三萬 點解要去做地盤咁撚辛苦"},{"pid":"28e124ccb904e5423715ea9b59d061802cbac44d","tid":1811450,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"803d8879327eb2da13de7733aabaf7ecaa4b22ee","tid":1811450,"uid":131839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9165a8315f871d745d7b17007322e5d847396230","tid":1811450,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"當然如果做到就梗係最好啦，不過要面對好多發展商啊地產商啦佢哋勾結，但我讚成搞返個黃色地產商與其將啲錢比大財團不如益返自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"岩啊 我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"好多發展商就係覺得自己財雄勢大，唔撚理你，如果搞得成，第一個收新鴻基皮啦，之後收撚埋美心皮，最後食埋怡和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0dda030c1e6c121ed6c6a77d5e8f41bff8feb5","tid":1811450,"uid":32586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"叫誠哥減價好過"}]}